Liverpool star Raheem Sterling took to Instagram to share another photo from his holiday.

The 20-year-old flew to Jamaica after the Reds drew 2-2 with Leicester on New Year's Day, and was also absent from Liverpool's 2-1 win over AFC Wimbledon in the FA Cup third round on Monday.

But he is set to return to action against Sunderland in the Premier League on Saturday lunchtime.

